<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="marvelous-adj">marvelous <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mɑːvələs/    美 /'mɑːrvələs/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-wonderful">1.<strong>非凡的；不可思议的 (wonderful)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No matter what happens, you’re going to have a marvelous time.
无论发生什么，你都会度过一段精彩的时光。</p><footer>外研⑦ – 6</footer></div></div>